  "description": {
    "zh": "出于某种原因，塔科夫的PMC们喜欢DMR，可疑的模式，你知道。你很可能也有很大罪责！我不怪你，朋友。这些武器非常出色，绝对惊人的枪！别以为我会因此恨你和你的伙伴们。\n\n但我联系你不是为了告诉你这个，而且你已经自己知道了。你需要现金、装备和枪，而我需要这些枪支的数据。所以你何不做你最擅长的事呢？我甚至会借你一些东西来完成工作，你觉得你能处理吗？如果你能完成任务，我会更加印象深刻。别担心，工作和报酬是匹配的。",
    "en": "For some reason PMCs here in Tarkov love DMRs, suspicious pattern, you know. You are likely very guilty here too! And I don't blame you, friend. These weapons are excellent, absolutely amazing guns! Don't think I'll hate you and your buddies for that.\n\nBut I wouldn't contact you to tell you that, besides you already know that yourself. You need cash, gear and guns, and I need data on these firearms. So why don't you do what you do best huh? I'll even lend you some stuff for the job, you think you can take care of it? I'd be more than impressed if you would complete your task. And don't worry, the job with match the payment."
  },
